There are 2174 rows as expected from looking at the text file. However there are some missing values, which will need imputing for the prediction. There are no anomalous values - wind from 1.4 to 22.2 m/s is plausible, similarly temperatures from - 7 to 29 The gas demand also looks plausible.

Impute missing data - using pandas time series interpolation

In [20]:
gas_src = gas_src.apply(lambda x: x.interpolate(method='time'), axis=0)
